<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 yǒu shí huì bèi rén lěng luò, yǒu shí huì bèi shì rén kuā,
 yǒu shí huì bèi rén yōng dài, yǒu shí huì bèi rén cháo mà,
 yào xué huì zěn yàng chù fēng fù, yào xué huì zěn yàng chù pín qióng,
 shēn biān de kùn nán bù yào zài hū ya, kào zhǔ jīn tiān huó de xiāo sǎ,
 yǒu zhǔ wǒ bù pà fēng chuī yǔ dǎ, yǒu zhǔ wǒ bù pà kǔ tòng zhēng zhā,
 zài yà bó lā hǎn de yǎn jīng lǐ, wǒ yǐ kàn dào le tiān shàng de jiā.</lyrics>
<title>kào zhǔ jīn tiān huó de xiāo sǎ 迦南236</title>
<hymn_number>236</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>